SUMMARY:2753 - Hawaiian Luau Party
DESCRIPTION:Bring island vibes to the kitchen in this lively\, hands-on Luau Party cooking class with Cat Alwine. Guests will cook\, sip\, and celebrate while learning to prepare comforting Hawaiian-inspired dishes rooted in tradition and bold flavor. This class is perfect for anyone who loves cooking\, culture\, and a good time. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up.  \n\nLomi Lomi Salmon\nMusubi\nLoco Moco\nButter Mochi
