DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exciting Asian Stir-Fry Cooking Class with our instructor\, Cat Alwine! Explore the bold and vibrant flavors of Asian cuisine as she teaches you the art of creating delicious stir-fry dishes. Learn the secrets to perfecting your stir-fry technique\, from selecting the freshest ingredients to mastering the balance of flavors and textures.  \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up.  \n\nFilipino Pancit\nKorean Japchae\nChinese Chop Suey
