DESCRIPTION:Gather your girlfriends and celebrate the season in this hands-on Springtime Girls’ Brunch cooking class with Chef Sophia Dickmyer. This class is all about light\, fresh flavors\, relaxed cooking\, and enjoying time together in the kitchen – the perfect way to welcome spring with good food and great company. \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 21 and up \n\nFruit Salad with Grapefruit Vanilla Syrup\nSour Cream and Onion Deviled Eggs\nCreme Brûlée French Toast\nBacon and Cheese Spinach Puffs\nStrawberry-Orange Mimosas
