DESCRIPTION:Indulge in the best of land and sea with Chef Joe Hall in this elegant\, hands-on class inspired by the great American steakhouse. Learn refined yet approachable techniques from perfectly seared steak to luxurious sauce-making that brings restaurant-level sophistication to your home kitchen.  \nHands on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up.  \n\nSteak Oscar with Hollandaise (Sous Vide Technique)\nAsparagus and Crab\nClassic Tiramisu
