SUMMARY:2763 - Sourdough Bagel Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Join Chef Ret Beiler for a Bagel Masterclass! In this 3-hour\, hands-on workshop\, you’ll learn the entire bagel-making process from start to finish. Chef Ret will guide you through kneading\, shaping\, boiling\, and baking for perfectly chewy\, golden bagels. Choose your favorite toppings and take some home to enjoy! \nPartial Hands-on. BYOB. Ages 16 and up. Vegetarian \n\nBagel Dough\nShaping techniques\nBoiling techniques\nBagel seasonings\nTake-Home Fresh Bagels
