SUMMARY:2766 - Kids Cooking Camp: Pasta\, Sauces and Salads (ages 7-15)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a Pasta Party Cooking Adventure with our amazing kids’ instructor and artist\, Gwen Eberly! In this hands-on summer camp\, young chefs will learn how to cook and mix pasta\, create colorful sauces\, and explore fun fillings and add-ins. Each day\, campers will practice new kitchen skills\, experiment with flavors and textures\, and build confidence as they create delicious\, customizable dishes in a relaxed and encouraging environment. \nHands on. Ages 7-15 \nDay 1 – 7/28 \n\nThree-Cheese Stuffed Shells \nMixed Greens\, Tomatoes and Cucumbers with Pesto Vinaigrette\nOatmeal Chocolate Chip Cookies\n\nDay 2 – 7/29 \n\nHomemade Pasta\nFresh Herb\, Butter and Lemon Sauce\nCaesar Broccoli and Kale Salad\nSnickerdoodle Cookies\n\nDay 3 – 7/30 \n\nLasagna – Vegetable or Meat\nSummer Crunch Salad with Buttermilk Dressing\nLemon Cookies
